    Reading symbols from /home/tomxue/mycode/0___GitHub/coredump/test...done.
    [New LWP 3628]
    Core was generated by `./test'.
    Program terminated with signal 11, Segmentation fault.
    #0  0x080483f4 in a () at test.c:6
