    (gdb) bt
    #0  0x080483f4 in a () at test.c:6
    #1  0x08048418 in main () at test.c:11
    (gdb) 


    if no coredump provided...

    tomxue@ubuntu:~/mycode/0___GitHub/coredump$ gdb test
